head.title:
Charter of A.D. 956. King Eadwig to Bath Abbey, and to Wulfgar, abbot;
                                grant of 30 hides at Tidenham, Gloucs., of which 3 are to
                                belong to the abbot

msItem.ab:
The Abingdon charters are printed in Chronicon Monasterii de Abingdon (Rolls
                                Series), Introduction p. viii. Also many by Kemble and Birch. Kemble 356;
                                    S 411
